# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Cybork (ReeF Bot) — Environment Variables Reference
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# HOW TO USE
# ──────────
#  Option A — .env file  : Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your values.
#  Option B — api.json   : Fill in the api.json file in the project root.
#  Option C — Panel vars : Set variables directly in Pterodactyl / Replit / Docker.
#
# PRIORITY (highest wins)
# ───────────────────────
#  Panel / system env vars  >  api.json  >  .env
#
# RULES
# ─────
#  • Never commit .env or api.json to version control — they contain secrets.
#  • Use this file (.env.example) as the canonical reference; keep it up to date.
#  • Lines starting with "#" are comments and are ignored.
#  • Required vars must be set or the launcher will refuse to start.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DISCORD
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# [REQUIRED] Your bot's authentication token.
# Where to find it: Discord Developer Portal → Your App → Bot → Token
# Never share this value with anyone.
DISCORD_TOKEN=


# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DATABASE  (PostgreSQL)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# [REQUIRED] Full PostgreSQL connection string.
# Format  : postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/DATABASE
# Replit  : Auto-provided — leave blank, Replit fills this in automatically.
# VPS     : Set this OR the individual PG_* vars below (not both).
# Pterodactyl: Set this in the server's environment variables tab.
DATABASE_URL=

# [OPTIONAL] Individual PostgreSQL connection parts.
# Use these ONLY if you are NOT using DATABASE_URL above.
# Replit provides these automatically alongside DATABASE_URL.
PGHOST=
PGPORT=5432
PGUSER=
PGPASSWORD=
PGDATABASE=


# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TOP.GG  (optional — bot listing & vote rewards)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# [OPTIONAL] Your Top.gg API token.
# Where to find it: https://top.gg/bot/<your-bot-id>/webhooks
# Leave blank to disable Top.gg stats posting and vote tracking.
TOPGG_API=
